Draft Resource Management Plan and Environmental Impact Statement, published December 2012
Theme: Special Recreation Management Area (SRMA)
Description: SRMAs by alternative. An SRMA is an administrative designation where a commitment has been made to emphasize recreation by managing for specific rec. opportunities and rec. setting characteristics on a long-term basis. RMZs (recreation management zones) delineate specific rec. opportunities.
